task.summary: Initial checkin. rollup, eslint, rest and rpc methods.
add rpc and rest test cases

refactor top level object 'neo.rest' and 'neo.rpc' to 'neo.antChain' and 'neo.node' as these are better descriptions of the api interfaces they implement. Rest and Rpc are low-level protocols which should be abstractions at the higher level. Services may implement one or more protocols.
update doc to match latest refactor of `neo.node`
Add capability to transform response payload to a data model instance
Add new service and api methods for antchain.xyz. Refactor for easier customization of protocolClient.
Add neon service, polling feature and examples. Updated tests.
refactoring, move 3rd party service endpoints to eco folder, create new builds for core only, and for both browser and nodejs, update tests.
add package-lock.json so all devs will get the same npm module versions
include dist folder for npm package
